- Use ShadCN UI components
- Follow accessibility guidelines

# File Naming

- Components: PascalCase (e.g., `MedicalRecord.tsx`)
- Utilities: camelCase (e.g., `formatDate.ts`)
- Types: PascalCase (e.g., `PatientTypes.ts`)
- Tests: `*.test.ts` or `*.test.tsx`
- Pages: kebab-case (e.g., `patient-records.tsx`)

